Hive Compression Technique
==============================================

compression will help you to save storage.
Also it will help to process the data faster.
It will reduce I/O cost.

Compression & Uncompression comes with some cost in terms of time taken to compress  and time to taken to uncompress.
When we compare it with I/O gains we can actually neglect this addtional time.

